<L>__{exterior sicilian landscape med. view day}
<A>__{across the slain body of a fourteen year old boy, lying on the parched ground. in the distance we see four or five of the mourning women, the wind blowing their black dresses and veils, running up to the body of the boy. they begin to wail, and cry out in anguished sicilian, as the widow, the mother of the murdered boy, holds her child in her arms, his fresh blood wetting her strong hands.}
